title: Print, ca. 1550
creditline: Gift of Eleanor and Sarah Hewitt
description: Composed of two half-figures of putti with plant scrolls in the northern style instead of legs, of three dogs on leashes, and a man.  Verso: The central part of nine lines of an Italian treatise on astronomy.
